Why rhythm is powerful for perception

Humans evolved to detect temporal patterns very efficiently.

Rhythm helps us:
	•	predict the next event
	•	coordinate movement
	•	filter signal from noise

In a sense, rhythm acts like a guide for attention, letting the brain anticipate what comes next.

